'''Yinchorri flutter-packs''' were unique packs with wings which allowed [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] to fly. These only could be used for one hour, then they needed to be recharged for eight hours before another use. They used them to move about on the [[Yibikkoror floating city|balloon city]] on the colony world of [[Yibikkoror]], as well as in their [[Raid on the Jedi Temple (Yinchorri Uprising)|attack]] on the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]].

